name: Grade 9 - [First Year]
description: Entry-level secondary education focusing on foundational subjects.

name: Grade 10 - [Second Year]
description: Builds on foundational knowledge with a more structured curriculum.

name: Grade 11 - [Third Year]
description: Introduces more specialized subjects and prepares students for advanced studies.

name: Grade 12 - [Fourth Year]
description: Final stage before advanced secondary education or pre-university level.

name: Grade 13 - [Fifth Year]
description: Advanced level studies with a focus on specialization and exam preparation.

name: Grade 14 - [Sixth Year]
description: Final preparatory year for higher education or professional training.
